<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/boundary-commission-for-scotland> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Boundary Commission for Scotland (BCS) carries out boundary reviews of parliamentary constituencies in Scotland, and submits its recommendations to the government. BCS is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Scotland Office ."@en .
